snippet.title: Maja Mabengeza
snippet.description:
You know those thoughts that pop up into your head when you watch a true crime video and you start debating with yourself? Those drove me insane , so one day I clicked ‘record’ and decided to share them with the world. 

Why did they choose X as their last meal?  What got them on the death row? (LAST MEALS)  What was the flip switch that made them turn to crime?! (GONE BAD) 

I thrive on structure and transporting you to the minds of the killers, in order for you to ask yourself how would your actions have led to a different outcome? 

Shoot any suggestions over to maja.mabengeza@gmail.com or tweet at @majasmeltdown
